    </td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="text-nowrap">3.3.3 Error Suggestion</td>
    <td>AA</td>
    <td>
        
        <br>
        <strong>It helps: </strong><br>
        <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG21/Understanding/error-suggestion.html" target="_blank">
            WCAG: Understanding 3.3.3: Error Suggestion
        </a>
    </td>
    <td>
        
